sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant WK as Worker
  participant AD as Adapter
  participant DB as MongoDB
  participant OP as Operator
  participant API as API

  WK->>AD: classify / embed
  AD->>AD: on_usage(model, category, input, output)
  AD->>DB: $inc daily rollup — date:provider:model:category
  OP->>API: GET /admin/usage
  API->>DB: rollup rows + conversation-derived chat/testing usage
  API->>API: price via pricing table → UsageBreakdown + month-to-date $
  API-->>OP: by provider / model / category + budget bar
  Note over WK,API: worker monitor raises llm_budget_exceeded at MTD ≥ LLM_MONTHLY_BUDGET_USD
